---
title: Greek-Style Chicken & Potato Salad with Garlic Yoghurt & Parmesan
description: Feeling like something fresh and tasty, low-carb and easy? May we present our Greek-style chicken flavoured with garlic. Tender and simply yum, resting on top of a crisp salad and sprinkled with cheese, this dish is perfect to ring in these warmer days (or any day for that matter)!

